conventions:
  - Code review: mandatory before merge to main
  - Testing: unit tests for core audio logic, integration tests for pipeline
  - Documentation: `///` doc comments for all pub items (Rust/Slint), enforced by scanner
  - Commits: semantic messages with scope (e.g., "feat(audio): add equalizer", "fix(ui): layout issue")
  - Branches: feature/ bugfix/ refactor/ naming
  - File limits: Rust max 300 lines, Slint max 200 lines
  - Layer tags: all types must carry layer suffix (_ui, _adp, _core, _pal, _gtw, _x)
  - English only: all code, comments, identifiers in English
